{
  "pcaconnectorad.template.subjectnameflagsv4.CfnAbout": "Information to include in the subject name and alternate subject name of the certificate. The subject name can be common name, directory path, DNS as common name, or left blank. You can optionally include email to the subject name for user templates. If you leave the subject name blank then you must set a subject alternate name. The subject alternate name (SAN) can include globally unique identifier (GUID), DNS, domain DNS, email, service principal name (SPN), and user principal name (UPN). You can leave the SAN blank. If you leave the SAN blank, then you must set a subject name.",
